      "span_text": "The first was the H-R172W line, which expressed the transgene at approximately 75% of the WT level and showed a severe, early-onset, dominant cone-rod dystrophy.  Here we describe the phenotype in an additional line (L-R172W) that expressed the transgene at approximately 40% of the WT level."
